comments: Bane (MEM) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Barrett's (NYK) arm that does not affect his SQBR.  He then places a marginal hand on Barrett's back.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) grabs and pulls Barrett's (NYK) jersey prior to the blocked shot and the contact affects his shot attempt at the rim.
Randle (NYK) extends his arm into Clarke's (MEM) upper body and grabs and pulls his jersey, affecting his ability to defend the pass.
Clarke (MEM) makes contact to Randle's (NYK) arm during the side-to-side motion of his rip-through and the foul occurs before he is considered to be in a shooting motion.
Quickley (NYK) moves forward into Morant (MEM) and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
Morant (MEM) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Burks' (NYK) lower body and he is able to maintain his dribble.
Clarke (MEM) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact to the body from Randle (NYK) during his shot attempt at the rim.  Marginal arm contact occurs when Randle extends his arm into Clarke's.
Replay review of the out-of-bounds called on Morant (MEM) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Morant saves the ball from going out of bounds.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes contact to Randle's (NYK) arm that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Jones (MEM).
Randle (NYK) commits a take foul on Jones (MEM).
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
